The above histogram shows that our data is not normally distributed, thus we would be using the 1.5xIQR method for detecting and eliminating outliers¶
In [140]:
percentile25 = lamudi_data.price.quantile(0.25)
percentile75 =  lamudi_data.price.quantile(0.75)
iqr = percentile75-percentile25
